			<tr>
			<td>
				<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="3"><b>    Pyzjin</b>&nbsp;<a href="../Subscribe.asp?DID=21067"><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></font>
					<br>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">
					<b><a href="mailto:dnimblett@msn.com">Raynos</a> | 
		                        1/5/2000 10:24:26 AM</b></font></p>
					
					<p>
					<font face="verdana" size="2">Well, I've been trying to gather as much information as I could about Pyzjin.  I hear he is a very rare spawn and drops a black stone of some sorts.  The purpose of this post is to find out whatever information you guys might have.  I'd love to know spawn times(I hear he's a random spawn between 4 and 12 hours), or his lvl, the use and worth of this stone and any other information I could use to track and hunt this NPC.  Thanks, and see ya on the Prexus server.
			<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>
					</p>
